      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUTTER ME UP (8) drew wide last start and was easily accounted for, beaten 10 metres into sixth at this track over 2130m. Will need a bit of luck negotiating a very wide starting position. Has the talent to take this out. AMERICAN FALCON NZ (11) made a nice return at his latest appearance two weeks ago, finishing 15 metres away in third over 2130m at this track. Should enjoy a nice smother from this draw and will be looking for a split at some stage. That latest effort is good enough to take out a race like this. WHEELSOFORTUNE (7) should be ready to peak now after finishing second over 2130m at this track two weeks ago. Expect him to give this a real shake. BROOKLANDS LAST (2) got home by 6 metres over 2130m at this track on debut four months ago. One to watch at her first run back.",
